Abengoa Completes Solar-Thermal Power Plant in India, First of Its Kind

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 
2011-09-26T11:44:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/abengoa-completes-solar-thermal-power-plant-in-india-first-of-its-kind.html
Abengoa SA (ABG) , the biggest Spanish
developer of solar-thermal power plants, completed a project in
 India  with a 3-megawatt capacity, the Seville, Spain-based
company said in a filing today. The plant can supply electricity
to about 1,000 households using a parabolic cylinder design, is
the first of its kind in India, Abengoa said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  